  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/86b0dc2639eb339c7d7ac3828ad18ec3.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/86b0dc2639eb339c7d7ac3828ad18ec3.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/86b0dc2639eb339c7d7ac3828ad18ec3.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This environment has been designed to ensure your well-being. Your cooperation is essential for the proper development of the experiment.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is SAFE ZONE?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SAFE ZONE</strong> is a narrative and psychological experience disguised as a platformer and puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simulation created to break you into pieces. And then see what you do with them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, death is not a failure. It's the only way forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game divided into chapters. Each one explores a new mechanic and a different fragment of a story you’re not required to understand, but it might remind you of something.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are Subject 42.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be guided by MARA, our artificial intelligence in charge of the experiment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She knows what you need. Even before you do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/c10511ea59630d0979380b3369485b1e.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/c10511ea59630d0979380b3369485b1e.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/c10511ea59630d0979380b3369485b1e.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Approximate duration: 20 minutes</u></i></strong><br><strong><i><u>Perfect run: 3 minutes</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 levels designed as tests of obedience, observation, and failure.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/738d0f97efa7d79629bf58d826429ee2.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/738d0f97efa7d79629bf58d826429ee2.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/738d0f97efa7d79629bf58d826429ee2.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main mechanic: die in traps to unlock the black door.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/1cfd353b77dbb967b9bca7a2a3cd2066.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/1cfd353b77dbb967b9bca7a2a3cd2066.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/1cfd353b77dbb967b9bca7a2a3cd2066.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each trap represents a way to die. Every death counts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order matters. Pain does too.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/89e85308a2ade69a044f0dd1467f23ad.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/89e85308a2ade69a044f0dd1467f23ad.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/89e85308a2ade69a044f0dd1467f23ad.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Approximate duration: 4 hours</u></i></strong><br><strong><i><u>Perfect run: 13 minutes</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New versions of the levels: 10 normal, 9 inverted, 10 negative.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/eabbd0cc969b5a63b90ab2c195c9ab99.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/eabbd0cc969b5a63b90ab2c195c9ab99.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/eabbd0cc969b5a63b90ab2c195c9ab99.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mechanic: defy the rules imposed by the system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introduction of the blue door and the concepts of \"perfection\" and \"speed.\"</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0807218bf5da37b7045e7f28ca29af4d.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0807218bf5da37b7045e7f28ca29af4d.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0807218bf5da37b7045e7f28ca29af4d.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasing difficulty and greater control in appearance, but less freedom.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 possible endings based on the player’s choices and skill.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>Current features of the experiment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/cdd4848be4891b1bd90b0db26d6bb323.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/cdd4848be4891b1bd90b0db26d6bb323.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/cdd4848be4891b1bd90b0db26d6bb323.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In development for the full version</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/87d53ce35b6f327d245b6e58585168dd.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/87d53ce35b6f327d245b6e58585168dd.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/87d53ce35b6f327d245b6e58585168dd.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0e0ee57c616f741e590b5320a245dede.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0e0ee57c616f741e590b5320a245dede.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0e0ee57c616f741e590b5320a245dede.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 rga nixinw.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vlgvg eti hvkiphu eph vlgvg eti grgqkiu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Qwpvmrpccgv kw psy exekpcfni.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vlg gqpqv kw psy ktigr.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧠 <strong>Who is this game for?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those who enjoy challenging platformers with unique mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those seeking a symbolic narrative that doesn't hand everything to you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For anyone who ever felt like they didn’t belong, and chose to keep playing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for participating.<br>Remember: in the end, everything will be fine. And if it’s not fine… it’s not the end.<br>— J.</p>",
