tatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/1cfd353b77dbb967b9bca7a2a3cd2066.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each trap represents a way to die. Every death counts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order matters. Pain does too.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/89e85308a2ade69a044f0dd1467f23ad.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/89e85308a2ade69a044f0dd1467f23ad.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/89e85308a2ade69a044f0dd1467f23ad.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Approximate duration: 4 hours</u></i></strong><br><strong><i><u>Perfect run: 13 minutes</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New versions of the levels: 10 normal, 9 inverted, 10 negative.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/eabbd0cc969b5a63b90ab2c195c9ab99.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/eabbd0cc969b5a63b90ab2c195c9ab99.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/eabbd0cc969b5a63b90ab2c195c9ab99.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mechanic: defy the rules imposed by the system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introduction of the blue door and the concepts of \"perfection\" and \"speed.\"</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0807218bf5da37b7045e7f28ca29af4d.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0807218bf5da37b7045e7f28ca29af4d.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/0807218bf5da37b7045e7f28ca29af4d.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasing difficulty and greater control in appearance, but less freedom.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 possible endings based on the player’s choices and skill.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>Current features of the experiment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/cdd4848be4891b1bd90b0db26d6bb323.poster.avif?t=1748945985\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/cdd4848be4891b1bd90b0db26d6bb323.webm?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3699100/extras/cdd4848be4891b1bd90b0db26d6bb323.mp4?t=1748945985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In development for the full version</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span